## Admin data model overview

Core admin-managed entities:
- Product
- ProductCategory
- Supplier
- PricingRule
- InstallationRule
- FinancingOption
- TaxRule
- LabourCost
- ProvinceConfig
- Lead
- Property
- Invoice
- Simulation
- Proposal

## Conversion philosophy

This platform should not stop at “leave us your details”.

Every lead should have an actionable next step. Depending on lead quality and technical complexity, the system should expose one or more of the following:
- book a call
- request proposal by email
- open WhatsApp with context
- reserve / contract online

Online contracting should be available only for cases that match predefined eligibility criteria.

## SEO strategy

The project should support scalable local SEO with dedicated landing pages such as:
- `/placas-solares-salamanca`
- `/placas-solares-avila`
- `/placas-solares-zamora`
- `/placas-solares-valladolid`

And intent-based pages such as:
- solar panels price
- solar panels with battery
- solar panels for homes with pool
- solar panels + aerothermal heating
- tax deduction for solar panels in Spain
- financing options

## Delivery roadmap

### Phase 1 — MVP
- marketing landing pages
- bill upload
- parser v1
- property questionnaire
- solar simulation v1
- proposal result page
- lead capture and action CTAs
- admin catalog management

### Phase 2 — Commercial hardening
- support for multiple invoices
- improved parsing templates
- financing comparison module
- proposal PDF generation
- CRM-style lead workflow
- province configuration

### Phase 3 — Conversion expansion
- online reservation / contracting flow
- e-signature
- payment / deposit
- advanced admin controls
- analytics and funnel optimization

## Success metrics

The project should track:
- organic traffic by province page
- calculator start rate
- bill upload completion rate
- simulation completion rate
- lead conversion rate
- call booking rate
- WhatsApp initiation rate
- proposal-to-sale conversion
- estimate accuracy versus final installed project

## Project principles

- Commercial-first
- Clear and credible calculations
- Strong local SEO foundation
- Admin-editable pricing and catalog
- Fast lead activation
- No overengineering in MVP
- Honest ranges instead of inflated promises

